ADDED

bash-static - https://github.com/robxu9/bash-static
curl-static - https://github.com/moparisthebest/static-curl
soar - https://github.com/pkgforge/soar?tab=readme-ov-file

INFORMATION

Added bash and also made it the default shell. However, you can still change it to Ash or Sh.
Added curl, command to run it is "curl".
Added soar as the package manager. More information on their website.
Example soar commands are - 
	soar install <package>
	soar remove <package1> <package2> <package3>
	soar update
	soar update <package1> <package2>
	soar search <query>

